data.description: Welcome to this beautifully renovated 5-bedroom, 3- bathroom, 2- car garage 2 story home in the highly desired community of Madison Green!! Appreciate your privacy on your over-sized corner lot and mature landscaping. Fall in love with entertaining with your grand foyer entrance featuring volume ceilings, custom built-in home entertainment center, modern fireplace, brand-new appliances, separate dining area and additional living area!  Brand new flooring and new paint throughout this home brings this bright, open, and modern feel for you to adore! Downstairs offers one bedroom and bathroom, great for guests. Upstairs you will find your spacious primary bedroom suite, which features a lovely additional sitting area, dual vanities, separate tub and shower.  The fifth bedroom is currently configured as a loft with closet and electrical already in place, just needs a wall. Take this experience outside through any of the three sliding glass doors to your private fenced-in backyard, large side yard, and patio area. Ashford Village is a gated community within Madison Green, which requires NO golf membership fees and a low HOA. Enjoy all of the resort style amenities, which offers golf course, tennis/basketball/pickleball courts, community pool & spa, splash pad, playground, gym, clubhouse, and bar/grill, and low HOA fee includes: Xfinity hi-speed internet, cable, and lawn irrigation water. Do not miss this incredible opportunity to make this home yours!
